quran[6{c,v,t}:
10,15,"jab inhen hamari saaf saaf baatein sُnayi jati hain to woh log jo hum se milnay ki tawaqqa nahi rakhtay, kehte hain ke “as ke bajaye koi aur quran lao ya is mein kuch tarmeem karo"" ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho “میرا yeh kaam nahi hai ke apni taraf se is mein koi tagayur o tabdal kar lon mein to bas uss wahi ka pairo hon jo mere paas bhaije jati hai agar mein apne rab ki nafarmani karoon to mujhe aik barray holnaak din ke azaab ka dar hai """
10,16,"aur kaho “agar Allah ki mushiyat nah hoti to mein yeh quran tumhe kabhi nah sunataa aur Allah tumhe is ki khabar taq nah deta aakhir is se pehlay mein aik Umar tumahray darmain guzaar chuka hon, kya tum aqal se kaam nahi letay ?"
10,17,"phir uss se barh kar zalim aur kon ho ga jo aik jhooti baat ghurr kar Allah ki taraf mansoob kere ya Allah ki waqai ayaat ko jhoota qarar day yaqeenan mujrim kabhi Falah nahi pa satke """
10,18,"yeh log Allah ke siwa unn ki parastish kar rahay hain jo un ko nah nuqsaan pouncha satke hain nah naffa, aur kehte yeh hain ke yeh Allah ke haan hamaray safarishi hain ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho “کیا tum Allah ko uss baat ki khabar dete ho jisay woh nah asmano mein jaanta hai nah zameen mein ?"" pak hai woh aur baala o bartar hai uss shirk se jo yeh log karte hain"
10,19,"ibtida saaray ensaan aik hi ammt thay, baad mein unhon ne mukhtalif aqeday aur maslak bana liye, aur agar tairay rab ki taraf se pehlay hi aik baat tey nah kar li gayi hoti to jis cheez mein woh baahum ikhtilaaf kar rahay hain is ka faisla kar diya jata"
10,20,"aur yeh jo woh kehte hain ke iss NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam par is ke rab ki taraf se koi nishani kyun nah utari gayi, to un se kaho “ghaib ka maalik o mukhtaar to Allah hi hai, acha, intzaar karo, mein bhi tumahray sath intzaar karta hon """
